{"tid":1721992,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）比拉鬼佬係嶺南學生，黑狗準備入hall","createTime":"2019-11-14T20:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:02:09.000Z","uid":3716,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04ec7cfce95888ca771c596c94ac402fa0651564","tid":1721992,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬係嶺南exchange就fc咗<br />\n但黑狗係咪要入hall就未confirm住<br />\n但如果要入hall其他同學就要收好文具啦<br />\n<br />\n有乜可能鬼佬都要搜屋<br />\n究竟佢係想查鬼佬定係想剷起嶺南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細剷起逐一將大學據點擊破<br />\n<br />\n小心大家"},{"pid":"dc60b980049ad8f6d84e6be08ab01b29f187fab6","tid":1721992,"uid":116146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:36:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcb449e064fb2f207186d8d276d2016acc2835c4","tid":1721992,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:37:14.000Z","msg":"鬼佬身上搜到文具？"},{"pid":"2dd9f21604e07388a20200ca8be34c3f4492cdf2","tid":1721992,"uid":3716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcb449e064fb2f207186d8d276d2016acc2835c4","tid":1721992,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:37:14.000Z","msg":"鬼佬身上搜到文具？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:38:53.000Z","msg":"唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話有嫌疑就係嫁啦"},{"pid":"f0ed220a757b3fbd1c240511e5fc34e7358a2108","tid":1721992,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dc9be923ea2505b34b80620b968770afd23b85","tid":1721992,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:45:58.000Z","msg":"鬼佬圖？"},{"pid":"4461cf1069342421489a7fee3550e4c54f48a180","tid":1721992,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:56:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"005441aa4804a8fbb08001f442cf1c4eb98f9d12","tid":1721992,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:03:21.000Z","msg":"傳左咁多次會搜都無做就會變狼來了。"},{"pid":"d21224b51e355bab2cc9424dfe8994fc20be4d8b","tid":1721992,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16bf67adf838e7e9d240e199a55b29fef0ba2c1","tid":1721992,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"魚翅航空無女<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2 分鐘前<br />\n【19:30】據了解，兩名被捕男子均為嶺南大學交換生。<br />\n<br />\n【17:28】反修例風波下各區有多人示威抗議，昨晚（14日）一批示威者在屯門鄉事會路與杯渡路交界聚集，警方到場展開驅散行動，並在屯匯街一巴士站截查兩名分別22及23歲外籍男子。<br />\n<br />\n經調查後，該名22歲外籍男子涉非法集結及違反《禁止蒙面規例》被捕，另一23歲外籍男子涉嫌非法集結被捕。二人正被扣留調查，案件交由屯門警區重案組人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}